text: Rebecca Louisa Ferguson Sundström (born 19 October 1983) is a Swedish actress and model. She is known for her role as Elizabeth Woodville in the British television miniseries The White Queen (2013). Ferguson starred as MI6 agent Ilsa Faust in the action spy movie Mission: Impossible – Rogue Nation (2015) and its sequels Mission: Impossible – Fallout (2018), and Mission: Impossible – Dead Reckoning Part One (2023). She played Jenny Lind in the musical The Greatest Showman (2017), and also starred in the comedy-drama Florence Foster Jenkins (2016). ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish movie actors Category:Swedish stage actors Category:Swedish television actors Category:Swedish voice actors Category:Actors from Stockholm
